==Hindi==
===Interrogative particle===
'''क्या''' (kyā)
# initial [[interrogative]] [[particle]]. In this usage, it does not have a direct translation as a word in English, it simply makes a statement into a question.
#:Example: क्या आप यहाँ रहते हैं? (kyā āp yahā̃ rehte haĩ?) "Do you live here?" or "[Question marker] You here live do?" in literal order.

===Interrogative pronoun===
'''क्या''' (kyā)
# [[what]]
#:Example: आम का दाम क्या है? (ām kā dām kyā hai?) "What is the price of mangos?" or "Mangos of price what is?" in literal order.

